    Blazorise Tailwind Usage
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Quickly install Blazorise with Tailwind, one of the world's most popular Blazor UI framework.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Blazorise Tailwind provider is made possible with the help of <Anchor To="https://flowbite.com/" Title="Link to Flowbite" Target="Target.Blank">Flowbite</Anchor>, an open-source Tailwind CSS Components.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageParagraph>
